  "id": "api/core/OnDestroy",
  "title": "OnDestroy",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L147-L177\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L147-L177\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/OnDestroy\", \"name\": \"OnDestroy\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ondestroy\">OnDestroy<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnDestroy#ondestroy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A lifecycle hook that is called when a directive, pipe, or service is destroyed.\nUse for any custom cleanup that needs to occur when the\ninstance is destroyed.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">一个生命周期钩子，它会在指令、管道或服务被销毁时调用。\n用于在实例被销毁时，执行一些自定义清理代码。</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/OnDestroy\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnDestroy</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/OnDestroy#ngOnDestroy\">ngOnDestroy(): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"descendants class\">\n    <h2 id=\"实现类\">实现类<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnDestroy#实现类\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n\n<ul>\n  \n    <li>\n      <code><a href=\"api/forms/AbstractFormGroupDirective\" class=\"code-anchor\">AbstractFormGroupDirective</a></code>\n      \n\n\n    </li>\n  \n    <li>\n      <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterPreloader\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterPreloader</a></code>\n      \n\n\n    </li>\n  \n    <li>\n      <code><a href=\"api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">UpgradeComponent</a></code>\n      \n\n\n    </li>\n  \n</ul>\n\n\n  </div>\n  \n\n</section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnDestroy#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">Lifecycle Hooks</a> guide</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\"><a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">生命周期钩子</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"方法\">方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnDestroy#方法\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngOnDestroy\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"ngondestroy\">\n        ngOnDestroy()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnDestroy#ngondestroy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L170-L176\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L170-L176\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">A callback method that performs custom clean-up, invoked immediately\nafter a directive, pipe, or service instance is destroyed.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">一个用于执行清理逻辑的回调方法，会在指令、管道、服务的实例被销毁后立即调用。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngOnDestroy(): void</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<p>没有参数。</p>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnDestroy#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">The following snippet shows how a component can implement this interface\nto define its own custom clean-up method.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">下列代码片段展示了组件如何实现该接口，以定义它自己的清理逻辑。</p>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'my-cmp', <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `...`})\nclass MyComponent implements <a href=\"api/core/OnDestroy\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnDestroy</a> {\n  ngOnDestroy() {\n    // ...\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/forms/AbstractFormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/FormArrayName\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupName\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/NgModelGroup\n - api/forms/NgSelectOption\n - api/forms/RadioControlValueAccessor\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - api/router/RouterOutlet\n - api/router/RouterPreloader\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/dynamic-component-loader\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/styleguide\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#template\n - api/core/OnDestroy#ngOnDestroy\n - api/core/OnDestroy#ngondestroy\n - api/core/OnDestroy#ondestroy\n - api/core/OnDestroy#see-also\n - api/core/OnDestroy#usage-notes\n - api/core/OnDestroy#实现类\n - api/core/OnDestroy#方法\n - api/forms/AbstractFormGroupDirective\n - api/router/RouterPreloader\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L147-L177\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L170-L176\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L147-L177\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L170-L176\n-->"
